[12:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'resolution images, then you can set this value to one. And then for anything lower, then you can set this to 0.5. But if it\'s lower, then you don\'t really need to use dysp. You can just use flux. Anyways, let\'s just keep it at the'

[12:40] [scene:talk]
